query:
SELECT c.id, c.name, c.trainerId, u.name as trainer_name
FROM clients c
LEFT JOIN users u ON c.trainerId = u.id
WHERE c.name LIKE '%test%' OR c.name LIKE '%Test%' OR c.name LIKE 'edit%' OR c.name LIKE 'delete%'
ORDER BY c.id;
